                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6711" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1050</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11862 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机遇与挑战——“国货之光”Insta360影石品牌持续发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Opportunities and Challenges - &quot;The Light of Domestic Products&quot; Insta360 Brand&#39;s Sustainable Development Road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谢庆红，王嘉馨，付晓蓉，朱兢，王鑫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">影石创新科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Insta360影石；智能影像设备；自主品牌；品牌发展；2022百优案例；重点项目；系列3-3</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Insta360; Intelligent Imaging Equipment; Self-owned Brand; Brand Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着户外运动热度持续走高，消费者对运动体验记录、日常拍摄与分享的需求井喷式增长，智能影像设备行业进入高速发展期。影石创新科技股份有限公司作为一家深圳本土企业，凭借先进的研发技术持续推出了多种创新性爆款产品，加速占领国内外市场，已成长为全球知名的智能影像企业。本案例分析了面对其他劲敌的冲击，Insta360影石如何实施自主品牌持续发展战略。通过梳理行业竞争格局，讨论了在消费端市场扩大顾客基数及提高复购率、企业端拓展垂直行业应用领域的业务、区域市场实现海内外共同发展的管理层决策建议。通过对本案例的学习，使学员能够分析企业的内部能力和外部环境因素，识别竞争者，根据品牌竞争位势准确制定品牌发展战略，提高学员将品牌发展理论运用于管理实践的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the increasing popularity of outdoor sports and the exponential growth of consumer demand for sports experience recording, daily shooting and sharing, the smart imaging equipment industry has entered a period of rapid development. As a local enterprise in Shenzhen, Arashi Vision Inc. has continuously launched a variety of innovative and popular products with cutting-edge technology, accelerated the occupation of domestic and foreign markets, and grown into a world-renowned intelligent imaging company. This case analyzes how Arashi Vision implements the strategic decision of the sustainable development of its self-owned brand Insta360 in the face of the impact of other competitors. By analyzing the competitive landscape of the industry, this case discusses the company&#39;s decision to expand the customer base and increase the repurchase rate in the consumer market, the development opportunities in the application field in the enterprise vertical industry, and the regional market layout to achieve the common development of domestic and overseas markets. Through the study of this case, students can analyze the internal capabilities and external environment of the company, identify competitors, and accurately formulate brand development strategies according to brand positions, and improve students&#39; ability to apply brand development theory to management practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《品牌管理》、《营销管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌发展的内外部环境因素；品牌的一般竞争战略类型、战略制定的因素；品牌的竞争位势；宏观环境下的品牌战略选择；品牌发展的路径和方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
